iven Sports kritisch zu hinterfragen gilt.  afunded by Swiss National Science Foundation (SNSF)  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aDiversität. 4aGender Studies. 4aGender. 4aGeschlecht. 4aHeteronormativität. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 4aKörper. 4aLeistungssport. 4aPraxistheorie. 4aQueer Theory. 4aSportwissenschaft. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Gender Studies.2bisacsh  aBody.  aCompetitive Sports.  aCultural Studies.  aDiversity.  aGender Studies.  aGender.  aHeteronormativity.  aPractice Theory.  aQueer Theory.  aSport Science.2 aSwiss National Science Foundation (SNSF)efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839442166zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de GruyterzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839442166zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839442166/original  a978-3-11-071955-0 DG Plus eBook-Package 2018b2018  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA